data.description: Come check out this awesome home, equipped with 3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, office / flex room could be used as a 4th bedroom, 2 1/2 car garage, this split floor plan is perfect for a family or someone looking to be in an established neighborhood. Located 1 mile from Broken Arrow high school and less than a mile to Country Lane Elementary, pond and pool amenities available, extended back patio, sprinkler system, professional landscaping in front and back, dog run, open concept and more.
